        "created_at": "2023-02-18T18:54:53.638Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I\u2019ve had 96 HB twice, and it\u2019s lovely (HB is my favorite wine), but it\u2019s not in the elite tiers of HB or FGs.  Pretty classic, elegant and mid weight.</p>",
